            <h3>What's the minimum age to obtain a driving licence in India?</h3>
            <p>One must be at least <strong><u>18 years</u></strong> of age to apply for a driver’s
                licence in India.However, one can also acquire driving licence after 16 years for vehicles upto 50CC with parental consent.
           </p>
