            <h3>How to renew my licence?</h3>
            <p>
                You can renew your driver’s licence online up to one year before and after the expiration date.
                 If you do not renew your licence within one year after this date, you will incur additional fees and also give driving skill test. 
                 Furthermore, you will not be able to renew your India licence if it has been expired for more than five years.
              </p>
