            <h3> Does RTO provide vehicle for road test?</h3>        
            <p>
                No. The applicant must bring his own vehicle. 
                It must correspond with the type of India driver’s licence he or she is obtaining.
                 For example, if applying for 2 wheeler driving licence, you cannot bring a four wheeler vehicle for the test.
            </p>
